sentences: Bobby Nunn (born 1952) is an American R&B music producer, songwriter and vocalist, best known for his top 15 US Billboard R&B chart hit single, "She's Just a Groupie".
Bobby Nunn co-produced his 1982 debut Motown album Second to Nunn, with Winston Monseque.
